## Featured Projects

###  Banner–Drupal Integration Portal
**Tech Stack:** Drupal 9, REST APIs, PL/SQL, Oracle DB  
**Summary:** Integrated Ellucian Banner with Drupal to create a student self-service portal. Developed custom modules to securely fetch and display academic records, registration status, and financial aid data.

- Built RESTful endpoints to expose Banner data
- Created role-based views for students, faculty, and staff
- Reduced support tickets by 40% through self-service access

