### Dynamic Course Catalog
**Tech Stack:** Drupal Views, Panels, Custom Content Types  
**Summary:** Designed a searchable, filterable course catalog for academic departments. Enabled real-time updates from Banner and improved UX for prospective students.

- Automated course sync via PL/SQL scripts
- Implemented taxonomy-based filtering
- Increased site traffic by 25% post-launch

