### Automated Form Workflows
**Tech Stack:** Oracle Forms, PL/SQL, Drupal Webforms  
**Summary:** Migrated manual admissions and financial aid forms into a hybrid system using Oracle Forms and Drupal Webforms. Enabled conditional logic and backend validation.

- Reduced processing time by 60%
- Improved data accuracy and compliance
